title: Nancy Walker - I Hate Men Vinyl 256kbps 1959
description:
That "quicker picker upper" Bounty spokeswoman, with Emmy and Tony nominations, Rhoda&#039;s mom Ida, yes... Nancy Walker with Sid Bass and his Orchestra. Songs of a scorned woman? No, just light hearted irritation of relationships, i guess. The title track was from "Kiss Me Kate", in fact all the songs are from broadway shows. Enjoy!
